description:
History

Origin

Monsteroso is a microscopic being who's entire world was small enough to fit on a single slide of a microscope in the laboratory of an unnamed professor. Monsteroso was hatched from an egg and continued to grow within his microscopic land until it began to flood with water around him. Unknown to Monstero an assistant by the name of Smith had taken the slide and placed it in the sink to wash unintentionally damning Monsteroso and his entire world.

Monsters Unleashed

Monsteroso was later seen during the invasion of the monstrous leviathans who were falling to Earth from outer space. How Monsteroso survived his watery death is unknown but he along with other Marvel Monsters appeared to combat these new threats that were dead set on destroying life on Earth.
name: Monsteroso

description:
Maya Dos Santos lives in Anaheim, California and lived a normal life. When she was introduced, she appears to be a 19 year old goth who lives a regular life, but struggled. It appears she is a college student and also is friends with another girl named Shilpa. Maya's mother is religious as well and wanted her daughter to go to mass that night. But Maya had other plans.

When she went to a club called the Black Vault, she couldn't get in because of her age.
name: Maya Dos Santos
